'''Neil Druckmann''' is a writer and creative director for the [[video game]] company [[Naughty Dog]].<ref>http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/articles/475066/20130605/last-interview-neil-druckmann-naughty-dog-ps3.htm</ref><ref>http://connecteddigitalworld.com/2013/05/27/the-last-of-us-exclusive-interview-with-neil-druckmann-from-naughty-dog/</ref><ref>http://www.playstationlifestyle.net/2013/06/21/the-last-of-us-single-player-dlc-is-a-side-story-first-draft-of-the-campaign-included-a-dog/</ref><ref>http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/video-games/10091838/The-Last-of-Us-interview-with-Neil-Druckmann-and-Ashley-Johnson.html</ref><ref>http://www.polygon.com/2013/6/7/4406144/last-of-us-world-is-ripe-for-more-stories-naughty-dog-neil-druckmann</ref><ref>http://www.el33tonline.com/spotlight/2013/06/18/the-last-of-us/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=the-last-of-us</ref>

==Works==
*''[[Uncharted 2: Among Thieves]]'' - writer and a lead game designer 
*''[[The Last of Us]] - creative director

